<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Alexie Pangilinan Portfolio</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial;
}

body{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9a9e,#fecfef,#fad0c4);
color:#333;
}

/* HEADER */

header{
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
color:white;
animation: fadeIn 2s;
}

header h1{
font-size:40px;
}

.typing{
border-right:3px solid white;
white-space:nowrap;
overflow:hidden;
width:22ch;
animation: typing 3s steps(22), blink .5s step-end infinite alternate;
margin:auto;
}

@keyframes typing{
from{width:0}
}

@keyframes blink{
50%{border-color:transparent}
}

/* NAVBAR */

nav{
background:white;
text-align:center;
padding:15px;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

nav a{
margin:15px;
text-decoration:none;
color:#ff4d88;
font-weight:bold;
transition:0.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
color:#ff0066;
font-size:18px;
}

/* SECTIONS */

section{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
padding:40px;
}

.card{
background:white;
width:70%;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
transition:0.4s;
animation: fadeIn 2s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

/* PROFILE */

.profile{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.profile img{
width:170px;
height:170px;
border-radius:50%;
border:6px solid #ff4d88;
object-fit:cover;
}

/* SKILLS */

ul{
list-style:none;
}

li{
padding:10px;
font-size:18px;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
color:white;
}

/* FADE ANIMATION */

@keyframes fadeIn{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(20px);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Alexie Pangilinan</h1>
<p class="typing">BSIT Student & Future Web Developer 💻</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#skills">Skills</a>
<a href="#projects">Projects</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="home">
<div class="card">

<div class="profile">
<img src="2v2pic.jpg">
</div>

<h2>Welcome 🌸</h2>
<p>Hello! I'm <b>Alexie Pangilinan</b>, a Bachelor of Science in Information Technology student. I enjoy exploring technology, creating simple websites, and learning programming to improve my skills.</p>

</div>
</section>

<section id="about">
<div class="card">

<h2>About Me ✨</h2>
<p>I am currently studying BSIT and I am passionate about technology and web development. I like designing websites and learning new digital skills that can help me grow in the IT industry.</p>

</div>
</section>

<section id="skills">
<div class="card">

<h2>Skills 💡</h2>

<ul>
<li> Web Design</li>
<li> HTML & CSS</li>
</ul>

</div>
</section>

<section id="projects">
<div class="card">

<h2>Projects 🚀</h2>

<ul>
<li>💻 Personal Portfolio Website</li>
<li>📚 Student Information System</li>

</ul>

</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<div class="card">

<h2>Contact 📩</h2>

<p>Email: alexiepangilinan94@gmail.com</p>
<p>Facebook:alexie pangilinan</p>

</div>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Alexie Pangilinan Portfolio 💖</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
